{
  "texts": [
    "In this work, we study WANDA (Sun et al., 2023), a particularly promising LLM pruning method, and its effects on model safety against jailbreak attempts.",
    "WANDA is a recently introduced pruning method that is computationally efficient, does not require any finetuning, and maintains good performance.",
    "Consider a linear layer W ∈ R Cout×C in, and a batched input X ∈ R T ×C in.",
    "In LLMs, T = N • L represents the total token count, where N is the batch size and L is the sequence length.",
    "WANDA assigns an importance score for each weight"
  ]
}